tip.text: Lasagne was well made with pasta cooked correctly, good sauce, slightly sweet, but thick, not dry. Good cheese and beef had no "by-products" in it. My opinion. 8 of 10.

On a scale of 1 -10, the Circus Burger is a 7. It was hot, juicy and the sauce and pickle slice were a good match. The beef patty was on the small side. Fries, nothing special. Jalapeño Poppers, good.
